{
  "stem": "4764.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then the Russians started coming in and taking over, and my father said it was time to start-- start somewhere new.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we-- he said it's time to go to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't get there for some reason from Romania, so he said the best thing would be go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we caught a train from Bucharest through-- [SIGHS] through Germany, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a fascinating thing, that the train went through Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- I couldn't understand why how come we, as Jews, could go through-- because there were no borders, in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no borders in between the different countries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was all in upheaval.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were people, I think, the different nation-- different nationalities we're grabbing as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the train actually went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we ended up in Paris, and this is where I went to school for the first time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Must have been the end of '45, '46.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to [INAUDIBLE] the first school, I suppose, for my equivalent age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just found it terribly odd, for some reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because they said, look, it was only last year, or the year before, when-- when we were there, when, you know, when you couldn't travel at all.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look how different it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't travel anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there you could actually get onto a train and travel without being whisked off the train and shot, deported, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just-- I think-- I think my parents actually marveled at this-- at this idea that this was now just so incredible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I think they imparted this-- this to me, that-- how different things were.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
